40faf5243ae7a8e11cea8f6fe9242486130b0b22.query:
update song
                            set metadata_modified_date = $2,
                            artist_id = (select artist_id from artist where artist_name = $3 limit 1),
                            song_title = $4,
                            album_id = (select album_id from album where album_name = $5 limit 1),
                            track_number = $6,
                            disc_number = $7,
                            song_year = $8,
                            song_month = $9,
                            song_day = $10,
                            duration = $11,
                            sample_rate = $12,
                            bit_rate = $13,
                            album_art_path = $14,
                            fingerprint = $15
                        where song_path = $1 and fingerprint != $15;

8c2c02dbdb900bcbdd52518bbba66950852240ba.query:
insert or ignore into song(
                            song_path,
                            metadata_modified_date,
                            artist_id,
                            song_title,
                            album_id,
                            track_number,
                            disc_number,
                            song_year,
                            song_month,
                            song_day,
                            duration,
                            sample_rate,
                            bit_rate,
                            album_art_path,
                            fingerprint
                            )
                            values
                            (
                                ?, ?,
                                (select artist_id from artist where artist_name = ? limit 1), 
                                ?, 
                                (select album_id from album where album_name = ? limit 1), 
                                ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?
                            );
